name: DELIVERY FLIGHT! WestJet 737 MAX 8 [C-FRAX] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Here we have WestJet's, and Canada's, very first Boeing 737 MAX 8 arriving at Calgary International Airport this afternoon. Those new engines sure look good. Despite the somewhat frosty relations between Boeing and Canada at the moment, it's cool to see this new aircraft. ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
